This track is for those doing Höhronen by public transport. Bus #10 from Oberägeri turns at Raten col, follow the small road to Gottschalkenberg to the small chapel Buschenchappeli. The trailhead is just beside a barbecue area and a small car park.
track_title: Ascent to the trailhead from Raten bus station
